This endpoint is used to check the KYC (Know Your Customer) status of a user. It sends an HTTP GET request to the specified URL. The request does not contain a request body.

### Response

- 404: The server could not find the requested resource. This could be due to an incorrect URL or the resource being temporarily unavailable.


#### Example Response

``` json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "data": {
        "kycDone": false
    }
}

 ```

